declarations.name: Default
declarations.default:
{
	render: ({ userTooltip, keywordTooltip, kind, postStyle, lang, withIcons }: BlockedContentProps) =>
		html`<blocked-content
			lang="${lang}"
			kind="${kind}"
			post-style="${postStyle}"

}
